{"tid":1210500,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"去一次修頓球場我就知道點解藍波俾人叫做玩具","createTime":"2019-06-12T13:54:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T04:11:41.000Z","uid":187192,"like":282,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"d6791f8b8fd36c199c79ceb2c6996d40d112fdb1","tid":1210500,"uid":187192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T13:54:08.000Z","msg":"買咗堆物資諗住去修頓球場俾咁多位義士<br />\n<br />\n結果淨係望到個足球場畀人用嚟存放物資<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yjEdwMp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyjEdwMp.jpg&h=fafe8ade&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但係另一邊廂既兒童遊樂場就仲有成班小朋友喺度玩玩具,國難當前仲喺度玩唔識分輕重真係火都嚟<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OzfL7kr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOzfL7kr.jpg&h=6369bf68&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ff6ca1f7f887951df8622a183d6d98aac1ff9fb1","tid":1210500,"uid":141176,"like":3,"dislike":62,"score":-59,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T13:54:57.000Z","msg":"樓主一定係矮仔 最多150<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aadb47a802a2b1bb18ed23f076ca62730ce12e27","tid":1210500,"uid":34572,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T15:28:29.000Z","msg":"唉......"},{"pid":"adfc7c0fc144e3cd9b25457315d9ae083865faa5","tid":1210500,"uid":5549,"like":62,"dislike":0,"score":62,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T16:15:53.000Z","msg":"玩得玩具既都係腦荀都未生埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"671400b5ffce31533d3f4ccbddff99505cbbeb89","tid":1210500,"uid":26959,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T16:18:44.000Z","msg":"唉..."},{"pid":"570ba1c2242c43dfbd7105f0f6ea26afa81d2b2e","tid":1210500,"uid":187192,"like":41,"dislike":1,"score":40,"quote":{"pid":"adfc7c0fc144e3cd9b25457315d9ae083865faa5","tid":1210500,"uid":5549,"like":62,"dislike":0,"score":62,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T16:15:53.000Z","msg":"玩得玩具既都係腦荀都未生埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T16:19:35.000Z","msg":"係<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n前面唔夠500米,有一班人就喺度為惡法抗爭, 班小朋友仲可以繼續面不改容喺度玩玩具,頭先仲以為自己去錯咗地方去左平行時空<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"456c7db94d8e154fe731fb5275736c29f27f8042","tid":1210500,"uid":130766,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T16:19:53.000Z","msg":"好在睇唔到我個樣"},{"pid":"ce06490abb1fe75de36d1d664f52aeb4658b668b","tid":1210500,"uid":187192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"456c7db94d8e154fe731fb5275736c29f27f8042","tid":1210500,"uid":130766,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T16:19:53.000Z","msg":"好在睇唔到我個樣"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T16:21:18.000Z","msg":"放心,特登拉遠咗先至影物資站"},{"pid":"17d22a7da02e0655d6a0be0eefd4ac584602da2b","tid":1210500,"uid":130766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T16:25:06.000Z","msg":"開頭足球場都有人用緊<br />\n不過開始多人個陣佢地好似散開比我地搬野"},{"pid":"6b94f12824a4cb14f29e6a2d5d9e1da2afad01f6","tid":1210500,"uid":209432,"like":31,"dislike":1,"score":30,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T16:25:55.000Z","msg":"咩時候仲喺度玩分化？<br />\n有冇諗過好多上前線嘅人就係你口中嘅玩具撚？<br />\n我睇你就真撚係腦筍未生埋喇"},{"pid":"3236e3f017771369eb1ad5c0850c167c2963a969","tid":1210500,"uid":232728,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T16:27:57.000Z","msg":"唔好搞分化啦好冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57affca2cf94d91d783e41394d63b3284bfc749e","tid":1210500,"uid":23451,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T16:30:19.000Z","msg":"藍波同足球個gag玩左好撚多年啦<br />\n唔好咁撚敏感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cl